# WhatsApp AI CRM — Workspace Rules

- Stack: Next.js 15, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Supabase
- Design system: Skeuomorphic (leather, brass, cream tones)
- Always use the `skeu-card`, `skeu-btn`, `skeu-input` CSS classes
- Database: Supabase (cpqtclqjppdcqmdnuizq.supabase.co)
- Never install new UI libraries without asking
- All pages go inside src/app/dashboard/
- Always use the cn() utility from @/lib/utils for classNames
